    public interface OpendaylightFlowTableStatisticsService
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.RpcService
    Interface for implementing the following YANG RPCs defined in module opendaylight-flow-table-statistics
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/opendaylight-flow-table-statistics.yang): 
     rpc get-flow-tables-statistics {
     "Fetch statistics of all the flow tables present on the tarnet node";
     input {
         leaf node {
             type node-ref;
         }
     }
     
     output {
         list flow-table-and-statistics-map {
             key "table-id"
             leaf table-id {
                 type table-id;
             }
             leaf active-flows {
                 type counter32;
             }
             leaf packets-looked-up {
                 type counter64;
             }
             leaf packets-matched {
                 type counter64;
             }
             uses generic-table-statistics;
         }
         leaf transaction-id {
             type transaction-id;
         }
     }
     status CURRENT;
 }
